data.description: Northpointe subdivision welcomes you. Nestled on a corner lot this charming home is looking for a new owner. Three bedrooms, two full baths, and a half bath. The main floor offers and oversized living room with vaulted ceilings, fireplace and plenty of windows to let in the natural light. The master suite is located on the first floor just off the living room with ample space for a king size bed and complimentary furnishings. Double sinks, garden tub and separate shower in the master bath. Two spacious bedrooms upstairs adjoined by a Jack and Jill bathroom. Enjoy summer days on your screened in porch. Roof replaced 2021, Water heater replaced 2021. Make an appointment today. Property will be available for viewing as of 06/30
